<section id="reference-wizards-hibernate_mapping_file">
  <title>Hibernate mapping file</title>
  <para>
    The Hibernate mapping file wizard automates the creation of mapping files for individual classes or all classes within a selected package or project. Once created the mapping files will be available for editing in the <guilabel>Tree</guilabel> view of the Hibernate mapping fil editor.
  </para>
  <figure id="figure-reference-wizards-hibernate_mapping_file_01">
    <title>The New Hibernate XML Mapping files wizard</title>
    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject>
        <imagedata fileref="images/image-hib-new_hibernate_xml_mapping_files_02.png" format="PNG"/>
      </imageobject>
      <textobject>
        <para>The New Hibernate XML Mapping wizard</para>
      </textobject>
  </mediaobject>
  </figure>
  <formalpara><title>Related material</title>
    <para>
      Further tasks and information relating to this wizard are accessible from:  <xref linkend="document_navigation-hibernate_mapping"/>.
    </para>
  </formalpara>    

